10:40.000 --> 10:41.000
<b>Sí.</b>

10:41.580 --> 10:43.330
<b>Entiendo.</b>

10:44.790 --> 10:46.040
<b>¿Sabes qué?</b>

10:46.120 --> 10:48.750
